; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/common/rails-routes.md

% rails-routes, common

# List all routes
rails routes

# List all routes in an expanded format
rails routes <__E___expanded_>

# List routes partially matching URL helper method name, HTTP verb, or URL path
rails routes <__g___grep_> <posts_path_GET__posts>

# List routes that map to a specified controller
rails routes <__c___controller_> <posts_Posts_Blogs__PostsController>
